<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Personal AI Playbook & Workflow Builder</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-main: #0f172a;
            --bg-card: #1e293b;
            --bg-input: #334155;
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --primary: #3b82f6;
            --primary-hover: #2563eb;
            --accent: #10b981;
            --border: #475569;
            --font: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-main);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: var(--font);
            line-height: 1.5;
            padding-bottom: 40px;
        }

        header {
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .logo { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }

        nav { display: flex; gap: 1rem; }
        nav button {
            background: none; border: none; color: var(--text-muted);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 0.375rem; transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        nav button.active { background-color: var(--primary); color: white; }
        nav button:hover:not(.active) { color: var(--text-main); background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }

        .help-btn { background: var(--bg-input); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-main); padding: 0.5rem 1rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; cursor: pointer; }

        main { max-width: 1200px; margin: 2rem auto; padding: 0 1rem; }

        /* Explainer Banner */
        .explainer-banner {
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        .explainer-banner h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--primary); }
        .explainer-banner p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-main); max-width: 90%; }
        .close-banner { position: absolute; top: 1rem; right: 1rem; background: none; border: none; color: var(--text-muted); cursor: pointer; font-size: 1.2rem; }

        /* General UI Elements */
        .card { background-color: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
        @media (max-width: 768px) { .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .header { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; } }

        h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        p.subtitle { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: -0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

        button.btn-primary { background: var(--primary); color: white; border: none; padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; width: fit-content; }
        button.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-hover); }

        select, input, textarea {
            width: 100%; background: var(--bg-input); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            color: var(--text-main); padding: 0.625rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: inherit;
        }

        /* Views */
        .view-section { display: none; }
        .view-section.active { display: block; }

        /* Interview Wizard */
        .mcq-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .mcq-option {
            background: var(--bg-input); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.375rem; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; text-align: left;
        }
        .mcq-option:hover { border-color: var(--primary); background: rgba(59,130,246,0.05); }
        .mcq-option.selected { border-color: var(--primary); background: var(--primary); }

        /* Prompt Blocks */
        .block-container { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; min-height: 100px; border: 2px dashed var(--border); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .prompt-block { background: var(--bg-input); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; position: relative; }
        .block-meta { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--primary); font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .block-desc { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .remove-block { position: absolute; top: 0.5rem; right: 0.5rem; color: #ef4444; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; }

        .block-picker { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
        .picker-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; }
        .picker-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }

        /* Live Preview & Output */
        .preview-box { background: #020617; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; font-family: monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 0.9rem; min-height: 120px; max-height: 300px; overflow-y: auto; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

        /* Workflow Items */
        .workflow-list { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
        .workflow-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
        .workflow-tags { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 0; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .tag { background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1); color: var(--primary); font-size: 0.75rem; padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; font-weight: bold; }

        /* Modal styling */
        .modal { display: none; position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); z-index: 1000; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
        .modal.active { display: flex; }
        .modal-content { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; max-width: 600px; width: 90%; position: relative; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">⚡ Personal AI Playbook</div>
        <nav>
            <button onclick="switchView('interview')" id="nav-interview">Setup Interview</button>
            <button onclick="switchView('dashboard')" id="nav-dashboard" class="active">Workflows Dashboard</button>
            <button onclick="switchView('prompt-builder')" id="nav-prompt-builder">Prompt Builder</button>
            <button onclick="switchView('loop-builder')" id="nav-loop-builder">Loop Builder</button>
        </nav>
        <button class="help-btn" onclick="toggleHelpModal(true)">❓ What is this?</button>
    </header>

    <main>
        <!-- Always Visible / Dismissible Onboarding Explainer -->
        <div class="explainer-banner" id="explainerBanner">
            <button class="close-banner" onclick="dismissBanner()">×</button>
            <h3>Welcome to your Modular AI System Engine</h3>
            <p>Instead of copying static prompts, this playbook builds custom, dynamic systems. Complete the <strong>Setup Interview</strong> to tailor options to your role, configure reusable blocks in the <strong>Prompt Builder</strong>, or design autonomous multi-step execution logic in the <strong>Loop Builder</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- VIEW: INTERVIEW WIZARD -->
        <section id="view-interview" class="view-section">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>AI Persona Tailoring Interview</h2>
                <p class="subtitle">Answer these simple questions to unlock highly structured prompts customized to your day-to-day work metrics.</p>
                
                <div id="interview-container">
                    <!-- Dynamic Question injection goes here -->
                    <h4 id="question-text" style="margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.15rem;"></h4>
                    <div class="mcq-grid" id="options-container"></div>
                    <button class="btn-primary" id="next-question-btn" onclick="submitAnswer()">Next Question</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- VIEW: DASHBOARD -->
        <section id="view-dashboard" class="view-section active">
            <div class="card">
                <h2>Your Curated Workflow Library</h2>
                <p class="subtitle">Your saved AI prompt workflows, at a glance. Filter, modify, or deploy instantly to your active LLM environment.</p>
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <input type="text" id="searchWorkflows" placeholder="Search saved patterns..." style="margin-bottom: 0;" oninput="renderDashboard()">
                    <select id="filterCategory" style="margin-bottom: 0; width: 250px;" onchange="renderDashboard()">
                        <option value="all">All Categories</option>
                        <option value="production">Production Systems</option>
                        <option value="evaluation">Quality Assurance</option>
                        <option value="loops">Autonomous Loops</option>
                    </select>
                </div>

